# Button

A customizable button component with multiple variants and sizes.

## Usage

```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";

<Button variant="default" size="md">
  Click me
</Button>
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| variant | `"default" \| "outline" \| "ghost"` | `"default"` | Visual style of the button |
| size | `"sm" \| "md" \| "lg"` | `"md"` | Size of the button |
| disabled | `boolean` | `false` | Whether the button is disabled |

## Variants

### Default

Primary button with filled background.

```tsx
<Button variant="default">Primary</Button>
```

### Outline

Button with border and transparent background.

```tsx
<Button variant="outline">Outline</Button>
```

### Ghost

Minimal button with hover effect.

```tsx
<Button variant="ghost">Ghost</Button>
```

## Accessibility

- Supports `aria-label` for screen readers
- Keyboard navigation enabled
- Focus visible by default
```

